  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/11689b4c7b4b745f67db60058942f40f.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=610 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/11689b4c7b4b745f67db60058942f40f.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/11689b4c7b4b745f67db60058942f40f.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Faraway Islands</strong> is a top-down 2D story-driven survival game, set on procedurally generated islands you can travel between and explore. The game features classic survival mechanics like crafting based on combining, gathering resources and food, farming, hunting animals, increasing character skills, building shelter, and defending against enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You <strong>play as a survivor</strong> of a passenger ship that sank in a wild storm. As you try to find a way home from these islands, you encounter new friends who will help you, and enemies giving you a hard time. (character visuals can be customized)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/dcb33bd460c8b64c6bc2032bfce37b78.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/dcb33bd460c8b64c6bc2032bfce37b78.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/dcb33bd460c8b64c6bc2032bfce37b78.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CRAFT TOOLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creating items is done by <strong>combining</strong> or processing items in your inventory. These combinations are not shown to the player from the start, so you have to try new combinations. Some are recommended to you by story characters or written in quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/7dcf9e30d0272b4a79c05a1eb353d67f.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-label=\"An animation of a player crafting a pickaxe in the inventory screen.\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/7dcf9e30d0272b4a79c05a1eb353d67f.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/7dcf9e30d0272b4a79c05a1eb353d67f.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CONSTRUCTION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can build your own <strong>shelter</strong> to ensure your safety from predators and enemies. The game has several basic buildings to choose from and construct, and more are unlocked by increasing your skills.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/20ddd474306201b76f115be0c54c52e2.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-label=\"An animation of a player building a campfire.\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/20ddd474306201b76f115be0c54c52e2.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/20ddd474306201b76f115be0c54c52e2.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE ISLANDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All islands are procedurally generated, which means everything from their shape to the number of crabs and mushrooms is randomly chosen and then created by predefined rules. Not all <strong>resources</strong> are the same on every island, so you must explore and find what you need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/24a5d0d8be038bf8ff918b24c457da2f.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-label=\"An animation of the in-game map.\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/24a5d0d8be038bf8ff918b24c457da2f.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/24a5d0d8be038bf8ff918b24c457da2f.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DANGER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild animals are dangerous, and you should be cautious when moving around them. So beware that pack of tigers can kill you quite quickly. There are also human <strong>enemies</strong> that will attack every few days. You can prepare for these situations by crafting weapons and armor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/c9de3afe69688135a466179ee00a44c8.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-label=\"An animation of a player chased by two tigers on a beach.\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/c9de3afe69688135a466179ee00a44c8.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/c9de3afe69688135a466179ee00a44c8.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/11689b4c7b4b745f67db60058942f40f.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=610 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/11689b4c7b4b745f67db60058942f40f.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/11689b4c7b4b745f67db60058942f40f.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Faraway Islands</strong> is a top-down 2D story-driven survival game, set on procedurally generated islands you can travel between and explore. The game features classic survival mechanics like crafting based on combining, gathering resources and food, farming, hunting animals, increasing character skills, building shelter, and defending against enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You <strong>play as a survivor</strong> of a passenger ship that sank in a wild storm. As you try to find a way home from these islands, you encounter new friends who will help you, and enemies giving you a hard time. (character visuals can be customized)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/dcb33bd460c8b64c6bc2032bfce37b78.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/dcb33bd460c8b64c6bc2032bfce37b78.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/dcb33bd460c8b64c6bc2032bfce37b78.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CRAFT TOOLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creating items is done by <strong>combining</strong> or processing items in your inventory. These combinations are not shown to the player from the start, so you have to try new combinations. Some are recommended to you by story characters or written in quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/7dcf9e30d0272b4a79c05a1eb353d67f.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-label=\"An animation of a player crafting a pickaxe in the inventory screen.\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/7dcf9e30d0272b4a79c05a1eb353d67f.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/7dcf9e30d0272b4a79c05a1eb353d67f.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CONSTRUCTION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can build your own <strong>shelter</strong> to ensure your safety from predators and enemies. The game has several basic buildings to choose from and construct, and more are unlocked by increasing your skills.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/20ddd474306201b76f115be0c54c52e2.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-label=\"An animation of a player building a campfire.\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/20ddd474306201b76f115be0c54c52e2.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/20ddd474306201b76f115be0c54c52e2.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE ISLANDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All islands are procedurally generated, which means everything from their shape to the number of crabs and mushrooms is randomly chosen and then created by predefined rules. Not all <strong>resources</strong> are the same on every island, so you must explore and find what you need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/24a5d0d8be038bf8ff918b24c457da2f.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-label=\"An animation of the in-game map.\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/24a5d0d8be038bf8ff918b24c457da2f.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/24a5d0d8be038bf8ff918b24c457da2f.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DANGER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild animals are dangerous, and you should be cautious when moving around them. So beware that pack of tigers can kill you quite quickly. There are also human <strong>enemies</strong> that will attack every few days. You can prepare for these situations by crafting weapons and armor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/c9de3afe69688135a466179ee00a44c8.poster.avif?t=1772456278\" aria-label=\"An animation of a player chased by two tigers on a beach.\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/c9de3afe69688135a466179ee00a44c8.webm?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/c9de3afe69688135a466179ee00a44c8.mp4?t=1772456278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
